{"tid":2340191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜文睪：周柏豪事件，證明你地要畀錢我","createTime":"2020-12-25T08:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T08:24:59.000Z","uid":76115,"like":20,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8499cd79d7b50f3ce842868f8f643990ec43d7b","tid":2340191,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"應承我，要課多啲畀拔萃男書院（英語：Diocesan Boys' School，簡稱男拔萃、男拔和DBS）畢業生牙杜（DBS仔）畀佢拖多啲糧。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/karma.dawa.7/posts/2114943298639573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkarma.dawa.7%2Fposts%2F2114943298639573&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=6a6c24f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/karma.dawa.7/posts/2114943298639573</a><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤<br />\n12月23日 13:00 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n其實周柏豪事件，正正反映到香港藝人本土發展嘅艱難，之所以我咁天真、咁辛苦都想做起個黃色娛樂圈就係咁解！<br />\n<br />\n嗰日我響台灣見到香港新聞，話王宗堯有困難，我唔開心咗幾日，咩事呀？做乜啫？！<br />\n<br />\n我噚日打俾杜太，叫佢約宗堯，同佢傾下長期合作計劃。無論到最後傾唔傾到都好，希望呢個post 出咗，會有人唔抵得我，出高價同我爭啦！<br />\n<br />\n正如我所講，喱騷收費台 <a href=\"http://www.lateshow.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lateshow.net&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=ea0201ef\" target=\"_blank\">www.lateshow.net</a><br />\n<br />\n嘅成立，唔單止係一個電視台，而係一個工程，希望你哋痛斥狗豪嘅同時，都支持下一啲靠香港人維生嘅藝人。"},{"pid":"ab5b0b77dad3fd0a9d91e757435886fa50a65ad5","tid":2340191,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"dea15e6e2c036da3596ce843c04e591f69e17891","tid":2340191,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"咁我幫緊呢個明星按摩，跟住佢揸我對波喎！知唔知跟住佢點呀？佢喺到唱：如真，如假，如打飛機可J自己😂😂 跟住我問：<span class=\"x-large\">咁你咪好感動囉</span>🤣🤣佢話：屌你啦😂😂&nbsp;<span class=\"x-large\">我張國榮fan來架</span>😂😂👍👍"},{"pid":"74c393e8cff3e9712509fa632ba52a8dc5615151","tid":2340191,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9743553277f06f57d7f2ffd02fa34db0e33d7e79","tid":2340191,"uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab5b0b77dad3fd0a9d91e757435886fa50a65ad5","tid":2340191,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔知你知唔知,&nbsp;其實杜汶澤係拔萃男書院(男拔)畢業,&nbsp;係一個男拔仔,&nbsp;所以好多出名男拔(DBS)畢業生都係佢師兄師弟或者同學,&nbsp;同佢一樣都係男拔(拔萃男書院)舊生"},{"pid":"63891ded1a14bdab8c2db3b70c94d7f21ff1a513","tid":2340191,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"課金支持"},{"pid":"705dab8dd4a9bad5d40550e207ba4910e5c59975","tid":2340191,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9743553277f06f57d7f2ffd02fa34db0e33d7e79","tid":2340191,"uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab5b0b77dad3fd0a9d91e757435886fa50a65ad5","tid":2340191,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔知你知唔知,&nbsp;其實杜汶澤係拔萃男書院(男拔)畢業,&nbsp;係一個男拔仔,&nbsp;所以好多出名男拔(DBS)畢業生都係佢師兄師弟或者同學,&nbsp;同佢一樣都係男拔(拔萃男書院)舊生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"知呀"},{"pid":"dbe3f7226437f811f296d88fb563b6c7cf7dad35","tid":2340191,"uid":303977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9743553277f06f57d7f2ffd02fa34db0e33d7e79","tid":2340191,"uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab5b0b77dad3fd0a9d91e757435886fa50a65ad5","tid":2340191,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔知你知唔知,&nbsp;其實杜汶澤係拔萃男書院(男拔)畢業,&nbsp;係一個男拔仔,&nbsp;所以好多出名男拔(DBS)畢業生都係佢師兄師弟或者同學,&nbsp;同佢一樣都係男拔(拔萃男書院)舊生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"所以？"},{"pid":"0fa68fc5f1c0a972ec67425a57454072da617a36","tid":2340191,"uid":252240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy